*herrie-1.8 (01 Jul 2007)

  01 Jul 2007; Robert Buchholz <rbu@gentoo.org>
  +files/herrie-1.8-chost.patch, +herrie-1.8.ebuild:
  Version bump, output default is now alsa. Upstream added pulseaudio support
  and greek locale

*herrie-1.7-r1 (05 Jun 2007)

  05 Jun 2007; Robert Buchholz <rbu@gentoo.org> -herrie-1.7.ebuild,
  +herrie-1.7-r1.ebuild:
  Changed a build option to remove noisy output when on ALSA/OSS.

*herrie-1.7 (03 Jun 2007)

  03 Jun 2007; Robert Buchholz <rbu@gentoo.org> +herrie-1.7.ebuild:
  Version bump:
  * Removed sdl support as it was completely broken
  * New swedish locale
  * removed scrobbler use flag and integrated it into USE=http
  * Jukebox mode

  12 May 2007; Robert Buchholz <rbu@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Added to sound herd

*herrie-1.6.1-r1 (30 Apr 2007)

  30 Apr 2007; Robert Buchholz <rbu@gentoo.org> -herrie-1.6.1.ebuild,
  +herrie-1.6.1-r1.ebuild:
  Install herrie.conf as .sample to conform with upstream intentions

